--- !u!114 &474352662
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 474352658}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e079d2f45fb5947fe9ac73f96a810dea, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: '::'
  wrath:
  - {fileID: 1548369186}
  - {fileID: 515594769}
  - {fileID: 1610482439}
  - {fileID: 2068454536}
  - {fileID: 2010104079}
  - {fileID: 1929636759}
  noScissorsInitial:
  - "Oh it\u2019s one of the few photos I have of all of us. Back when we used to
    be a family. After my son\u2019s funeral, we haven\u2019t even contacted each
    other."
  - My husband. He was the one who caused all of this.
  - 'Never present. He was always out at work, never cared for me and the kids and
    how we were doing. '
  - "It\u2019s no wonder things turned out this way. He left me to handle the family
    all on my own. Abandoned me."
  - "I can\u2019t stand the sight of his face. I need something to cut him out of
    this photo, only then will it be beautiful again."
  hasScissorsInitial:
  - "Oh it\u2019s one of the few photos I have of all of us. Back when we used to
    be a family. After my son\u2019s funeral, we haven\u2019t even contacted each
    other."
  - My husband. He was the one who caused all of this.
  - 'Never present. He was always out at work, never cared for me and the kids and
    how we were doing. '
  - "It\u2019s no wonder things turned out this way. He left me to handle the family
    all on my own. Abandoned me."
  - "I can\u2019t stand the sight of his face. I can use the scissors I found to
    cut him out of the photo, only then will it be beautiful again."
  final:
  - "There we go. It\u2019s now beautiful."
  ripHusband: {fileID: 1502879283}
  cutout_photo: {fileID: 2989677146848356056, guid: 021db6d1743611948983177a6123862e, type: 3}
  audioSource: {fileID: 1672729496}
  textAppears: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 903af894e42db4eab960334575b2c4d8, type: 3}
  interactSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7e221b2a6534e42708a92f828883ca75, type: 3}
  finishedDialogue:
  - I'm glad I never have to see his ugly face again.
