  greed:
  - {fileID: 1149433973}
  - {fileID: 1435585086}
  - {fileID: 1018494776}
  - {fileID: 1803698713}
  - {fileID: 815014595}
  - {fileID: 356486766}
  luxuryMakeup:
  - God. I bought so many high-end beauty products.
  - "I saw all the other mom\u2019s buying them so of course I couldn\u2019t let
    them look down on me. I have so many now they don\u2019t even fit anywhere anymore.
    They\u2019re mostly unopened."
  - "Still, I heard a new collection came out. I can\u2019t be made fun of for not
    having it. I\u2019ll have to buy it soon."
  audioSource: {fileID: 1672729496}
  textAppears: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 903af894e42db4eab960334575b2c4d8, type: 3}
  interactSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7e221b2a6534e42708a92f828883ca75, type: 3}
  finishedDialogue:
  - I need to look into that new collection. I don't regret any of my purchases.
