  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FurnaceInteract
  noMail:
  - What a nice furnace. I have no reason to turn it on though. Cold is mental.
  hasMatches:
  - Eh, might as well.
  hasMail:
  - "I\u2019ll just throw this in here."
  - I hope their stupidly decorated house burns down, just like the photo.
  burnedMail:
  - I don't regret anything I've done.
