  initial:
  - A nice assortment of kitchen tools. Spatula, spoon, scissors. Funny, makes it
    seem like I really cook.
  getScissors:
  - "I\u2019ll take these scissors. They can be very useful for opening things and
    cutting them up, amongst other things. "
  audioSource: {fileID: 1672729496}
  interactSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7e221b2a6534e42708a92f828883ca75, type: 3}
  finishedDialogue:
  - I don't feel like cooking. I won't be using these anytime soon.
