--- !u!114 &1938555334
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1938555329}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f0fe6a464ccd540eab009651e07b50a1, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::BoxInteract
  initialHasNothing:
  - "I\u2019ve been meaning to unpack these last few boxes. Just haven\u2019t gotten
    the energy to get around to it. "
  - "I\u2019ll need something sharp to open them up."
  openingBox:
  - Ok, now that I found these scissors, I can open this box up.  I can't keep putting
    it off.
  - "My son\u2019s old flower painting is in here. I remember he gifted it to me
    for my birthday before he passed. "
  - "I remember he went through a phase were he wanted to be an artist. I\u2019m
    glad I got him to get over that. Then he wouldn\u2019t have accomplished all
    that he did while he was alive."
  - "Never mind that. There\u2019s more stuff in here."
  findingAward:
  - "Oh! It\u2019s my son\u2019s academic excellence award. I\u2019ll put this right
    here so anyone who comes through will see how great he was."
  award: {fileID: 554299946}
  art: {fileID: 336173890}
  openBoxWithStuff: {fileID: -3165505885771590563, guid: 667c34b215f7d204ab626686bfd84f09, type: 3}
  openBoxEmpty: {fileID: 5562697346314754563, guid: 667c34b215f7d204ab626686bfd84f09, type: 3}
  pride:
  - {fileID: 1110892584}
  - {fileID: 352835687}
  - {fileID: 1872816054}
  - {fileID: 1121730296}
  audioSource: {fileID: 1672729496}
  textAppears: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 903af894e42db4eab960334575b2c4d8, type: 3}
  interactSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7e221b2a6534e42708a92f828883ca75, type: 3}
  finishedDialogue:
  - I'm glad I forced him to give up that preposterous art dream, now at least he
    has something to prove his legacy.
